<li id="cite_note-2"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-2">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite class="citation web cs1"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://mit.irr.org/brigham-young-we-must-believe-in-slavery-23-january-1852">"Brigham Young: We Must Believe in Slavery (23 January 1852)"</a>. March 6, 2014.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Brigham+Young%3A+We+Must+Believe+in+Slavery+%2823+January+1852%29&amp;rft.date=2014-03-06&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fmit.irr.org%2Fbrigham-young-we-must-believe-in-slavery-23-january-1852&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMormonism+and+slavery" class="Z3988"></span></span>
