<li id="cite_note-launiusr-7"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-launiusr_7-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-launiusr_7-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-launiusr_7-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite class="citation web cs1"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://launiusr.wordpress.com/2012/10/08/the-reorganized-church-of-jesus-christ-of-latter-day-saintscommunity-of-christ-and-african-american-members/">"The Reorganized Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints: Community of Christ and African-American members"</a>. October 8, 2012.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=The+Reorganized+Church+of+Jesus+Christ+of+Latter-day+Saints%3A+Community+of+Christ+and+African-American+members&amp;rft.date=2012-10-08&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Flauniusr.wordpress.com%2F2012%2F10%2F08%2Fthe-reorganized-church-of-jesus-christ-of-latter-day-saintscommunity-of-christ-and-african-american-members%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMormonism+and+slavery" class="Z3988"></span></span>
