<li id="cite_note-Child-13"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Child_13-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Child_13-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Child_13-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Child_13-3"><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFBlakemore2018" class="citation web cs1">Blakemore, Erin (November 14, 2018). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.history.com/news/native-american-slavery-mormon-utah">"Mormons Tried to Stop Native Child Slavery in Utah. They Ended Up Encouraging It"</a>. <i>The History Channel</i>. A&amp;E Television Networks, LLC.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=The+History+Channel&amp;rft.atitle=Mormons+Tried+to+Stop+Native+Child+Slavery+in+Utah.+They+Ended+Up+Encouraging+It&amp;rft.date=2018-11-14&amp;rft.aulast=Blakemore&amp;rft.aufirst=Erin&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.history.com%2Fnews%2Fnative-american-slavery-mormon-utah&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMormonism+and+slavery" class="Z3988"></span></span>
